      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore. everything is just... it's all falling apart. the climate, the politics, the way everything feels so broken. it feels like we're just watching a slow motion car crash and there's nothing anyone can do to stop it. how are you even supposed to care about building a life or a future when the foundation is literally rotting?",
